{"tid":1314390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[埋身技巧] 近距離作戰技巧，有用","createTime":"2019-07-14T06:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T07:42:14.000Z","uid":59618,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ad555b9810a40945659c85b013615306fe9922","tid":1314390,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:51:43.000Z","msg":"本人自細對武術有少少研究，玩開西洋拳，以前學過中國功夫，跆拳道。有少少知識想分享下，希望幫到大家。<br />\n對於d狗有頭盔，有棍，有甲既時候，得少少護具難免受傷，但係最重要既係減輕受傷同控制到對方。<br />\n<br />\n1. 通常d狗會拉起揸棍既手，煩似貼去背隻，因為咁樣大力好多。<br />\n你要做既係向住果隻手衝過去，<span style=\"color: red;\">你同佢既距離越近，佢既能力越低</span>，你越小機會比佢打傷。相反，千奇唔好向第二邊走，例如佢右手用棍，唔好去佢左邊，一定要去佢左邊，即係揸棍果個方向。你試唸下，佢一手揸盾，一手揸棍，控制到佢棍果邊佢就冇能力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 向低發展<br />\n當自己唔敢十分近既時候。例如對方一直揮棍，你可以向低發展。佢地通常有護腳，但護腳係唔包關節，其實好簡單，斜少少踩落去膝頭哥落少少既位，唔洗好大力佢而經跪係到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過緊去遊行，之後再繼續打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98f53b4c019ba45f2eba2315c8b05041fd64a67","tid":1314390,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:53:12.000Z","msg":"1 on 1 咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbb57443834207f5726ca13ace50e6db8703428","tid":1314390,"uid":59618,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f98f53b4c019ba45f2eba2315c8b05041fd64a67","tid":1314390,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:53:12.000Z","msg":"1 on 1 咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:57:56.000Z","msg":"唔關事，你見d狗用棍既時候就會拉開少少距離。要做既野好簡單就係唔好比佢拉開距離。"},{"pid":"d90fdd286908801d798dd16c7773f200c6e33601","tid":1314390,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6cbb57443834207f5726ca13ace50e6db8703428","tid":1314390,"uid":59618,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f98f53b4c019ba45f2eba2315c8b05041fd64a67","tid":1314390,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:53:12.000Z","msg":"1 on 1 咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:57:56.000Z","msg":"唔關事，你見d狗用棍既時候就會拉開少少距離。要做既野好簡單就係唔好比佢拉開距離。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你同正面嗰個近距離啫<br />\n<br />\n但佢左右兩邊既黑警可以打你架嘛  夠哂距離 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d389edb3053ee707433a2d6e80d635014fe0aeb0","tid":1314390,"uid":267801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"托手踭"},{"pid":"10be2a75bdbe2480027a0c8d05e9cfa56576aed9","tid":1314390,"uid":201407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"拉近左，佢附離2隻狗捉9你味仆得街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6687c1d0634646253bf5b8c6a0398d6c033ef4e3","tid":1314390,"uid":255563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:05:42.000Z","msg":"教撚壞人 直播見到啲人拎盾 就算係紙皮盾<br />\n都好有用"},{"pid":"978ec83f199cd80ecf95bb288792c3d1aaee876e","tid":1314390,"uid":238551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:25:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"310cadcaa52c84a6c72cac5fe3de558ac5f3600c","tid":1314390,"uid":28831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10be2a75bdbe2480027a0c8d05e9cfa56576aed9","tid":1314390,"uid":201407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"拉近左，佢附離2隻狗捉9你味仆得街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:29:21.000Z","msg":"呢d當然自己勇武人多或者有狗落單1on1個陣先做<br />\n冇人叫你一個走去打人一隊人咁on9"},{"pid":"ca97ce0e41d78ee2